The paper discusses the use of deep learning algorithms for the numerical solution of high dimensional PDEs, specifically Kolmogorov PDEs with affine drift and diffusion coefficients. This topic falls under the category of numerical analysis (cs.NA) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the application of these methods in finance and engineering, which could fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), systems and control (cs.SY), and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE).
